📄 LAAS24 – Product Requirements Document (PRD)
🧠 1. Product Overview

LAAS24 is a modern multi-vendor eCommerce platform designed for the Somali market and scalable globally.

It enables individuals to:

Create their own online store
Upload and manage products بسهولة
Share store and product links
Sell through WhatsApp and in-app chat

The platform combines:

Marketplace browsing (like Amazon)
Social selling (WhatsApp-based orders)
AI-assisted product creation
🎯 2. Objectives
Allow users to create a store in under 2 minutes
Enable vendors to upload unlimited products (based on plan)
Provide a fast, optimized product marketplace
Enable WhatsApp-based ordering flow
Provide AI tools for product creation
Support 10K+ daily active users without performance issues
👥 3. User Roles
🔹 Customer (Buyer)
Register / Login
Browse all products (homepage marketplace)
Filter products (category, price, location)
View product details
Contact vendor via:
WhatsApp (primary)
In-app chat (optional)
Place order request
Track orders
Leave rating & feedback
🔹 Vendor (Store Owner)
Register account
Create store profile
Upload products
Manage products
Receive order requests
Share:
Store link
Product links
Chat with customers
Use AI product assistant (premium)
🔹 Admin
Approve vendor registrations
Manage users and stores
Monitor products
Control subscriptions
Platform analytics
