Themes:
Light mode
Dark mode

🎨 Typography & Design System
Fonts:
Headings: Plus Jakarta Sans (premium, startup-style; weights 600–800 for titles)
Body: Inter (clean, readable; weights 400–700)
Design principles:
Minimal, spacious layout with consistent vertical rhythm
High contrast for headings; body text optimized for long reading (relaxed line-height)
Soft elevation: subtle shadows on cards and hover states
Rounded UI: border-radius approximately 12px–16px on cards and primary controls
Color system:
Primary: Green (brand / logo)
Secondary: Yellow/Gold (accents, badges)
Background: White or light gray (light); deep neutral (dark)
Theme support: Light and dark mode with the same token structure

